OL,3,CHarvey Weinstein taken to hospital for
OL,4,Cemergency heart surgery
OL,6,FDisgraced former film producer Harvey
OL,7,FWeinstein has been taken from prison
OL,8,Fto hospital for emergency heart
OL,9,Fsurgery, a spokesperson for his lawyer
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FThe 72-year-old was taken to the
OL,13,Fhospital from the Rikers Island jail
OL,14,Fin New York, where he is being held in
OL,15,Fcustody.
OL,17,FWeinstein's legal representative,
OL,18,FCraig Rothfield, told ITV News that
OL,19,FWeinstein was taken to hospital on
OL,20,FSunday night and underwent a procedure
OL,21,Fon his heart on Monday.
