OL,3,CHarvey Weinstein taken to hospital for
OL,4,Cemergency heart surgery
OL,6,FMr Rothfield confirmed Weinstein is
OL,7,Fout of surgery and in recovery.
OL,9,FHe added: "As we have extensively
OL,10,Fstated before, Mr Weinstein suffers a
OL,11,Fplethora of significant health issues
OL,12,Fthat need ongoing treatment."
OL,14,FWeinstein is serving a prison sentence
OL,15,Ffollowing a rape and sexual misconduct
OL,16,Fconviction in Los Angeles related to
OL,17,Fan incident in 2013 where he appeared
OL,18,Funinvited in a woman's hotel room
OL,19,Fduring a Los Angeles film festival.
