OL,6,FHe was sentenced to 16 years in prison
OL,7,Fin February 2023.
OL,9,FHe is currently in custody in Rikers
OL,10,FIsland jail complex while awaiting a
OL,11,Fretrial in Manhattan after a 2020
OL,12,Fconviction for rape was overturned
OL,13,Fearlier this year in a majority
OL,14,Fdecision from the Court of Appeal in
OL,15,FNew York.
OL,17,FIn July, Weinstein was treated in
OL,18,Fhospital after being diagnosed with
OL,19,Fpneumonia in both lungs, and Covid.
